_:Naf266cb0741e440c939b291bd175a005 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Rachel Blake MP was appointed as Parliamentary Secretary (Economic Secretary to the Treasury) in HM Treasury on 14 May 2026.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the MP for Cities of London and Westminster in July 2024.</p>\n" .
